data.description: **** PRICE ADJUSTMENT ****Sellers providing a $5K credit towards closing costs AND 1-year Home Warranty (Sheild Complete) through American Home Shield***. This large two-story house is located in the beautiful golf and country club community of Heritage Isles in New Tampa.  This spacious house is located on a corner lot with much to offer!  As you enter the house the foyer opens up to the 2nd floor with a 2nd floor foyer overlooking the front entrance with a large window bringing in lots of natural light.  As you walk in, to the right is the living room/dining room combo. The two areas are separated with columns and arches giving each space its individuality with plenty of room for entertaining.  As you make your way through the entry way hall you enter the family room/kitchen/eat in area with 1 guest bedroom and 1 full bath all located downstairs. Large sliders off the eat in area leading out to a covered patio. Lots of storage space on the first floor including a 3-car tandem garage. Upstairs includes 3 quest bedrooms, 1 quest bath, laundry room, Master bedroom with large en suite offering 2 separate vanities, a large stand-up shower and a garden tub for relaxation after a long day at work.  If this wasn't enough, the 2nd floor also offers a large bonus room with double doors that can be used as a game, additional family or movie room!!  The house was REPAINTED in 2020 and a NEW ROOF was installed in 2021! This house is perfect for a large or growing family!  The community offers golf, a large country club for gathering and entertainment with restaurant, a pool for relaxation and exercise, large fitness center, playground, park and tennis. The house is located minutes away from I-75, nearby shops, restaurants, movie theater, including Wiregrass Mall and the Tampa Premium Outlets, family game entertainment and much more. Don't miss out on this perfect opportunity! This house and location are a must see!
